413
00:43:10,719 --> 00:43:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, kakva je realna stopa odgovora na CRM kampanju?

414
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to deset posto?

415
00:43:16,239 --> 00:43:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to petnaest posto?

416
00:43:17,519 --> 00:43:18,719
