455
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:22,320
[SPEAKER_00] Vau.

456
00:46:22,880 --> 00:46:22,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

457
00:46:23,679 --> 00:46:26,480
[SPEAKER_00] I tako, znate, razmišljate o svemu što je uloženo u to.

458
00:46:26,719 --> 00:46:28,960
